data.description: Sought after Mott Park ranch now available! This 2 bed home features hardwood floor throughout living space, original wood trim and doors, as well as a windowed front porch. This home has 2 full baths, one on the main floor and one in the partially finished basement.  New furnace and air condition installed (2021), hot water tank(2017), an attic restoration(2021), as well as an updated kitchen(2023). Located directly across the street from Kettering University, this home is just munities away from downtown Flint, highways and amenities. There is a fully fenced back yard, detached one car garage and cement driveway. This home wont be around for long, schedule your private tour today!
